stress_overthinking.title: Mayaeet ak Kabwatutik
responses: Mayaa yan kanamin kabwatutik kamun koiibe tuguk che chang
Nkibwat soiti koyoi tabuuk kobur kouon ech ako maech
Malasima itatuan tuguk tugul raa
Nyolu ipos banda asi komuny akilit
Wii mutyo kamun iite kora

anxiety_worry.title: Arogenet ak Saitage
responses: Matibekach arogenet kumutin
Ibus nguni imi ole karan
Saitage kabwatutik ko ma imanit
Iime ge borto amun en kabwatutik beku ko maloo
Kiribuni tuguk che uu chu, imuche isir inono koraa

sadness_low_mood.title: Mabaibai ak Ng’wani
responses: Mayaa komakibaibait sait agee maboru kole megim
Malasima ibur kuoan ibaibai yon amii
Tuguk cheuyen ko mobure koigeny
Tuguk che ikose ko bo maana okot ko mogere biik alak
Nyolu isich kaliet ak ribet

loneliness_isolation.title: Kityon ak Aningen
responses: Kotikose kouan imii kityon ko mamanishani imii kityon
Chomin biik soiti kosir yeibuate
Kichomin kora okot yekose kouan mebaibai
Chang biik che kose kouni ma inyegen
Takobwane biik che iguyen ko uu ye iu

family_conflict_relationships.title: Kongwan ak Boyot
responses: Nan kongwan kot mayaa yon moguye gee
Nyolu kegonin tekisto ak kengalalun komiee
Yaan kabit kesit kengolole ak kiguiyo ge
Nyolu iriib tekisto
Kisobe yaan kabit kesit mainyegen ne kose kingwan

self_esteem_confidence.title: Anyokor ak Makonye
responses: Mewalaksei iiguu chii ake amun en makosa cha kayaiyak
Imuche akinyee iyai tuguk che achen
Matichokyi gee teiigu chito neo
Nyolu iboiboenchi gee
One hard moment doesn’t define your entire value.

academic_work_burnout.title: Sukul ak Keringet
responses: Igile gee okot ngot ikose kouon karinget
Koto karinget ko boru kole koigil kee
Kamunget ko karan yoon karigil gee
Malasima kokararanit tuguk tugul asi isir
Karan kimuny amun ii chito akinye

guilt_regret.title: Nyoet ak Kaat
responses: Yoe chitugul amkosa kinete gee mutyo
Iyanat inyoji gee kat
Koto mebaibai kewelesei
Makiwaale tuguk che kigoiyayak lakini walaksei tuguk che tomo
Nyolu isich nafsi agee akinye nyolu kosich chiitugul

trauma_emotional_pain.title: Nwanindo ak Muguleldo
responses: Che kiribunu kongwan en imanit
Beku ngwanindo ngopendi betusiek
Makaran ikas kiinwan kityon
Iigim kosir tuguk che kiyiyak
Asi kesob ketesetaa mutyo mutyo

motivation_stuck.title: Chorirenet ak Kibendi
responses: Saige kegose kouan kagenget yon kagouit soboni
Manyolu iyay tuguk che achen chemengek kobo maana kora
Meibuti inyee ko kenget kityo
Kotitindoi taabuk ko makilelen iburee kounoton kila
Teiboibaitu kochin gee sait
